                            <h1>
                            Es verdadero, &iquest;no es as&iacute;? Entonces, &iquest;qu&eacute; importa lo dem&aacute;s?
                            </h1>
                            <section class="author">
                                     <figure class="head-shot">
                                          <noscript class="lazy" data-alt="Neil L. Andersen" data-desktop="/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/neil-l-andersen-10.jpg">
